sequenceDiagram
    actor A as Admin
    participant FM as FormMutasi
    participant MC as MutasiController
    participant DK as DataKaryawan
    participant DM as DataMutasi

    A->>FM: Pilih Jabatan Baru & Submit()
    FM->>MC: ProsesMutasi()
    MC->>DK: UpdateJabatanDanDivisi()
    DK-->>MC: Return: Jabatan Diperbarui
    MC->>DM: CatatRiwayatMutasi()
    DM-->>MC: Return: Riwayat Tersimpan
    MC-->>FM: Tampilkan Alert Sukses()
